<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <title>About | Broch & Co.</title>
    <%- include('partials/head') %>
</head>
<body>
    <%- include('partials/nav') %>

    <section class="page-hero">
        <h1>About Broch & Co.</h1>
        <p>Setting the standard for elite household staffing across the Gulf and Caucasus.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="about-content">
        <div class="about-grid">
            <div>
                <h2>Our Story</h2>
                <p>Founded in Dubai, Broch & Co. was born from a clear need: families relocating to or residing in Georgia and Armenia deserved access to the same caliber of household professionals they relied on in the Gulf, Europe, and Asia.</p>
                <p>We specialize in sourcing, vetting, and placing experienced Filipino household professionals — nannies, private chefs, and executive housekeepers — for families who expect nothing less than excellence.</p>
            </div>
            <div>
                <h2>Our Approach</h2>
                <p>Every placement begins with understanding your family's unique needs, schedule, and household culture. We then draw from our curated network of pre-vetted professionals, each with verified experience and references from international placements.</p>
                <p>Our team handles all logistics: visa processing, Worknet registration in Georgia, Armenian work permits, travel arrangements, and onboarding — so you can focus on what matters.</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="stats-row">
            <div class="stat">
                <span class="stat-number">500+</span>
                <span class="stat-label">Placements Made</span>
            </div>
            <div class="stat">
                <span class="stat-number">3</span>
                <span class="stat-label">Countries Served</span>
            </div>
            <div class="stat">
                <span class="stat-number">98%</span>
                <span class="stat-label">Client Retention</span>
            </div>
            <div class="stat">
                <span class="stat-number">24/7</span>
                <span class="stat-label">Support Available</span>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <%- include('partials/footer') %>
</body>
</html>
